data.description: Beautiful 2-Bedroom, 1.5-Bathroom Property - Ideal for Investors or First-Time Homebuyers!  Are you searching for the perfect real estate opportunity? Look no further! This charming property offers everything you've been looking for, whether you're an investor seeking a hassle-free rental income or a first-time homebuyer eager to make your homeownership dreams come true.  2 Bedrooms: Spacious and comfortable bedrooms offer plenty of room for relaxation and rest.  1.5 Bathrooms: Enjoy the convenience of a full bathroom plus an additional half bath for guests.  Tenant in Place: This property comes with a reliable tenant already in place, ensuring an immediate return on your investment.Don't miss this fantastic opportunity to own a property that offers both immediate rental income and the potential for future appreciation. Schedule a viewing today and see for yourself the value this property has to offer!
